-- Gillard Says She Wants to `Wreck the People Smuggling Trade' to Australia
-- Gemma Daley
-- 2010-07-06T01:22:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-06/gillard-says-she-wants-to-wreck-the-people-smuggling-trade-to-australia.html

          
          
             Australian Prime Minister Julia
Gillard said her government would introduce policies to
strengthen border protection and “wreck” the people smuggling
trade. Gillard made the comments during a speech in Sydney
today.  
          
          


  


        